{"id":97,"parent_id":80,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":97,"title":"Mosiah 17","subtitle":"","short_title":"Mosiah","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 17"],[".studySummary",["i","Alma believes and writes the words of Abinadi—Abinadi suffers death by fire—He prophesies disease and death by fire upon his murderers. About 148",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.1","order":"05.19.017.10272"},["b","1"],"And now it came to pass that when Abinadi had finished these sayings, that the king commanded that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"priests"],"should take him and cause that he should be put to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"death"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.2","order":"05.19.017.10273"},["b","2"],"But there was one among them whose name was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Alma"],", he also being a descendant of Nephi. And he was a young man, and he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"believed"],"the words which Abinadi had spoken, for he knew concerning the iniquity which Abinadi had testified against them; therefore he began to plead with the king that he would not be angry with Abinadi, but suffer that he might depart in peace."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.3","order":"05.19.017.10274"},["b","3"],"But the king was more wroth, and caused that Alma should be cast out from among them, and sent his servants after him that they might slay him."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.4","order":"05.19.017.10275"},["b","4"],"But he fled from before them and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"hid"],"himself that they found him not. And he being concealed for many days did",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"write"],"all the words which Abinadi had spoken."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.5","order":"05.19.017.10276"},["b","5"],"And it came to pass that the king caused that his guards should surround Abinadi and take him; and they bound him and cast him into prison."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.6","order":"05.19.017.10277"},["b","6"],"And after three days, having counseled with his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"priests"],", he caused that he should again be brought before him."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.7","order":"05.19.017.10278"},["b","7"],"And he said unto him: Abinadi, we have found an accusation against thee, and thou art worthy of death."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.8","order":"05.19.017.10279"},["b","8"],"For thou hast said that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"God"],"himself should come down among the children of men; and now, for this cause thou shalt be put to death unless thou wilt recall all the words which thou hast spoken evil concerning me and my people."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.9","order":"05.19.017.10280"},["b","9"],"Now Abinadi said unto him: I say unto you, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"not"],"recall the words which I have spoken unto you concerning this people, for they are true; and that ye may know of their surety I have suffered myself that I have fallen into your hands."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.10","order":"05.19.017.10281"},["b","10"],"Yea, and I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"suffer"],"even until death, and I will not recall my words, and they shall stand as a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"testimony"],"against you. And if ye slay me ye will shed",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"innocent"],"blood, and this shall also stand as a testimony against you at the last day."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.11","order":"05.19.017.10282"},["b","11"],"And now king Noah was about to release him, for he feared his word; for he feared that the judgments of God would come upon him."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.12","order":"05.19.017.10283"},["b","12"],"But the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"priests"],"lifted up their voices against him, and began to accuse him, saying: He has reviled the king. Therefore the king was stirred up in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"anger"],"against him, and he delivered him up that he might be slain."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.13","order":"05.19.017.10284"},["b","13"],"And it came to pass that they took him and bound him, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"scourged"],"his skin with faggots, yea, even unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"death"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.14","order":"05.19.017.10285"},["b","14"],"And now when the flames began to scorch him, he cried unto them, saying:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.15","order":"05.19.017.10286"},["b","15"],"Behold, even as ye have done unto me, so shall it come to pass that thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"seed"],"shall cause that many shall suffer the pains that I do suffer, even the pains of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"death"],"by fire; and this because they believe in the salvation of the Lord their God."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.16","order":"05.19.017.10287"},["b","16"],"And it will come to pass that ye shall be afflicted with all manner of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"diseases"],"because of your iniquities."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.17","order":"05.19.017.10288"},["b","17"],"Yea, and ye shall be smitten on every hand, and shall be driven and scattered to and fro, even as a wild flock is driven by wild and ferocious beasts."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.18","order":"05.19.017.10289"},["b","18"],"And in that day ye shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"hunted"],", and ye shall be taken by the hand of your enemies, and then ye shall suffer, as I suffer, the pains of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"death"],"by fire."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.19","order":"05.19.017.10290"},["b","19"],"Thus God executeth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"vengeance"],"upon those that destroy his people. O God,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"receive"],"my soul."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.20","order":"05.19.017.10291"},["b","20"],"And now, when",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Abinadi"],"had said these words, he fell, having suffered death by fire; yea, having been put to death because he would not deny the commandments of God, having sealed the truth of his words by his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"death"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.1a","order":"05.19.017.10292"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-priesthoods"},"TG False Priesthoods"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.1b","order":"05.19.017.10294"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/26.11"},"Jer. 26:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.2a","order":"05.19.017.10296"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/23.9"},"Mosiah 23:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.2b","order":"05.19.017.10298"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26.15"},"Mosiah 26:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.11"},"Alma 5:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.4a","order":"05.19.017.10300"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/17.3.1-16"},"1 Kgs. 17:3 (1–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/13.13.13,22"},"Ether 13:13 (13, 22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.4b","order":"05.19.017.10302"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.6a","order":"05.19.017.10304"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.5"},"Mosiah 11:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.8a","order":"05.19.017.10306"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.27"},"Mosiah 7:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.34"},"13:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.9a","order":"05.19.017.10308"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courage"},"TG Courage"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/integrity"},"Integrity"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.10a","order":"05.19.017.10310"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"TG Persecution"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.10b","order":"05.19.017.10312"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/testimony"},"TG Testimony"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.10c","order":"05.19.017.10314"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/26.15.14-15"},"Jer. 26:15 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.13"},"Lam. 4:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/14.11"},"Alma 14:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/60.13"},"60:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.12a","order":"05.19.017.10316"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.5"},"Mosiah 11:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.25.17,25"},"12:25 (17, 25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.12b","order":"05.19.017.10318"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/20.2"},"Prov. 20:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.13a","order":"05.19.017.10320"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/3.6"},"Dan. 3:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/5.10.10-11"},"James 5:10 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/14.26.20-27"},"Alma 14:26 (20–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.13b","order":"05.19.017.10322"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.28"},"Mosiah 7:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/21.30"},"21:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/25.11"},"Alma 25:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.15a","order":"05.19.017.10324"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.10"},"Mosiah 13:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/25.12.7-12"},"Alma 25:12 (7–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.15b","order":"05.19.017.10326"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/25.5"},"Alma 25:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.16a","order":"05.19.017.10328"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.60.25-60"},"Deut. 28:60 (25–60)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.18a","order":"05.19.017.10330"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/25.8"},"Alma 25:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.18b","order":"05.19.017.10332"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.10"},"Mosiah 13:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/19.20"},"19:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/25.11.7-12"},"Alma 25:11 (7–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.19a","order":"05.19.017.10334"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/125.3"},"Ps. 125:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.19b","order":"05.19.017.10336"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/23.46"},"Luke 23:46"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.59"},"Acts 7:59"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.20a","order":"05.19.017.10338"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.26"},"Mosiah 7:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.20b","order":"05.19.017.10340"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.16.16-17"},"Heb. 9:16 (16–17)"],"."]]}
